    <h1>Trigger-Based Marketing</h1>
    <p class="description">Automated marketing communications sent the moment a specific customer behaviour occurs. Trigger-based messages are <strong>3-5x more effective than batch campaigns</strong> because they arrive at the exact moment the customer is most receptive.</p>
